Basic Installation
==================

NOTE: this will change in future versions: all files should belong to a 
special user, say 'lincs' and all users on the system should be part of 
group 'lincs'. User's 'lincs' account should be special: no shell, no login 
possible, etc. This is work in progress. 

3 easy steps:

    ./configure
    make

If this step fails because X11 headers are installed on your system, then
comment out HAVE_X11 in tvision/include/tv/configtv.h and 
    make clean
    make

Switch to root and enter:

    make install


Components
----------

- the 'tiger' binary will go in the default lincs installation directory,
   /etc/lincs/bin 

